('World of Alice   Pirate Treasure', 1526, 'World of Alice - Pirate Treasure World of Alice - Pirate Treasure is an educational game developed for children with the aim of developing logical reasoning through a map that contains the path to pirate treasure in a fun way from your cell phone, tablet or computer. Excellent educational resource. Game developed by: Nau.kids', 'Click on the answer corresponding to the treasure path', 'English'),
