('Skibidi Toilet Move Face', 1735, 'Welcome to Skibidi Toilet Move Face casual games, where youll embark on a journey in epic battlefield with brave warrior. These Casual Merge Games bring exquisite model and scene, immersing battle master in the strategic challenges between monsters and warriors. In Monster Battle toilet games, take on the role of a strategic Battle Master, defeating toilet warriors by synthesizing fight monster! Toilet games emphasize thinking, make key decisions that affect victory or defeat! In this Monster Battle casual game, battle master players use resources to build a army and engage in Monster Battle.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
